# 测试规范

## 单元测试

### ViewModel 测试

```kotlin
class AppViewModelTest {
    private lateinit var viewModel: AppViewModel
    private lateinit var mockPhotoService: PhotoService
    
    @Before
    fun setup() {
        mockPhotoService = mockk()
        // 设置 ViewModel
    }
    
    @Test
    fun `loadPhotos should update photos state`() = runTest {
        // Given
        val photos = listOf(Photo(...))
        coEvery { mockPhotoService.getAllPhotos() } returns photos
        
        // When
        viewModel.loadPhotos()
        
        // Then
        assertEquals(photos, viewModel.photos.value)
    }
}
```

### Service 测试

```kotlin
class PhotoServiceTest {
    private lateinit var photoService: PhotoService
    private lateinit var mockRepository: PhotoRepository
    private lateinit var mockHttpClient: HttpClient
    
    @Test
    fun `uploadPhoto should return success when upload succeeds`() = runTest {
        // Given
        val photoData = byteArrayOf(1, 2, 3)
        val expectedUrl = "https://example.com/photo.jpg"
        
        // When
        val result = photoService.uploadPhoto(
            photoData = photoData,
            fileName = "photo.jpg",
            mimeType = "image/jpeg",
            width = 1920,
            height = 1080
        )
        
        // Then
        assertTrue(result.isSuccess)
        assertEquals(expectedUrl, result.getOrNull()?.url)
    }
}
```

## 网络测试

### Mock HttpClient

```kotlin
class AuthServiceTest {
    @Test
    fun `login should return success with valid credentials`() = runTest {
        // Given
        val mockResponse = ApiResponse(
            code = 200,
            message = "Success",
            data = LoginResponse(...)
        )
        
        // Mock HTTP client
        // ...
        
        // When
        val result = authService.login(LoginRequest("user@example.com", "password"))
        
        // Then
        assertTrue(result is ApiResult.Success)
    }
}
```

## Compose UI 测试

### Screen 测试

```kotlin
@Composable
fun PhotosScreenTest() {
    val viewModel = mockk<AppViewModel>()
    every { viewModel.photos } returns MutableStateFlow(emptyList())
    
    PhotosScreen(viewModel = viewModel)
    
    // 验证 UI 元素
}
```

## 存储服务测试

### Mock 存储服务

```kotlin
class StorageServiceTest {
    @Test
    fun `uploadPhoto should return URL on success`() = runTest {
        val mockService = mockk<StorageService>()
        coEvery { 
            mockService.uploadPhoto(any(), any(), any(), any())
        } returns Result.success("https://example.com/photo.jpg")
        
        val result = mockService.uploadPhoto(...)
        assertTrue(result.isSuccess)
    }
}
```

## 测试工具

### 推荐库

- `kotlinx.coroutines.test` - 协程测试
- `mockk` - Kotlin Mock 框架
- `turbine` - Flow 测试
- `junit` - 测试框架

## 测试覆盖率

### 目标覆盖率

- 核心业务逻辑：≥ 80%
- Service 层：≥ 70%
- Repository 层：≥ 60%
- UI 层：≥ 50%

## 最佳实践

1. **测试隔离**：每个测试应该独立，不依赖其他测试
2. **清晰命名**：测试方法名应该描述测试场景
3. **AAA 模式**：Arrange-Act-Assert
4. **Mock 外部依赖**：网络、数据库、文件系统等
5. **测试边界情况**：空值、异常、边界值

## 注意事项

- ⚠️ **不要测试实现细节**：测试行为，不是实现
- ⚠️ **避免过度 Mock**：只 Mock 外部依赖
- ⚠️ **保持测试快速**：单元测试应该在毫秒级完成
- ⚠️ **测试失败消息**：提供清晰的失败消息
